{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.1","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:1","prev_osis_id":"Mic.005.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Proc\u00e8s de l\u2019\u00c9ternel avec son peuple. La mis\u00e9ricorde de l\u2019\u00c9ternel<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-5: cf. J\u00e9 2:4-7. 1 S 12:7-12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\u00c9coutez donc ce que dit l\u2019\u00c9ternel:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">L\u00e8ve-toi, plaide devant les montagnes,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et que les collines entendent ta voix!\u2026<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.2","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.5.14","name":"Mich\u00e9e 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.5.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.2","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:2","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>\u00c9coutez, montagnes, le proc\u00e8s de l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et vous, solides fondements de la terre!<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Car l\u2019\u00c9ternel a un proc\u00e8s avec son peuple,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Il veut plaider avec Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.3","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.3","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:3","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Mon peuple, que t\u2019ai-je fait?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">En quoi t\u2019ai-je fatigu\u00e9?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">R\u00e9ponds-moi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.2","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.4","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:4","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Car je t\u2019ai fait monter du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je t\u2019ai d\u00e9livr\u00e9 de la maison de servitude,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et j\u2019ai envoy\u00e9 devant toi Mo\u00efse, Aaron et Marie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.3","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.5","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:5","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Mon peuple, rappelle-toi ce que projetait Balak, roi de Moab,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ce que lui r\u00e9pondit Balaam, fils de Beor,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">De Sittim \u00e0 Guilgal,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Afin que tu reconnaisses les bienfaits de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.4","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.6","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:6","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.007,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 6-8: cf. Ps 50:7, etc.; 51:18, 19. \u00c9s 1:11-19. Os 6:6.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Avec quoi me pr\u00e9senterai-je devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour m\u2019humilier devant le Dieu Tr\u00e8s-Haut?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Me pr\u00e9senterai-je avec des holocaustes,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Avec des veaux d\u2019un an?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.7","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.5","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.7","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:7","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel agr\u00e9era-t-il des milliers de b\u00e9liers,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Des myriades de torrents d\u2019huile?<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Donnerai-je pour mes transgressions mon premier-n\u00e9,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Pour le p\u00e9ch\u00e9 de mon \u00e2me le fruit de mes entrailles?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.8","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.8","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:8","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>On t\u2019a fait conna\u00eetre, \u00f4 homme, ce qui est bien;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Et ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel demande de toi,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">C\u2019est que tu pratiques la justice,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Que tu aimes la mis\u00e9ricorde,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et que tu marches humblement avec ton Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.9","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.7","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.9","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:9","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-16: cf. (Am 8:4-8; 5:11-13.) 1 R 9:6-9.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>La voix de l\u2019\u00c9ternel crie \u00e0 la ville,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et celui qui est sage craindra ton nom.<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Entendez la verge et celui qui l\u2019envoie!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.10","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.8","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.10","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:10","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Y a-t-il encore dans la maison du m\u00e9chant<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Des tr\u00e9sors iniques,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et un \u00e9pha trop petit, objet de mal\u00e9diction?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.11","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.9","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.11","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:11","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Est-on pur avec des balances fausses,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et avec de faux poids dans le sac?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.12","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.10","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.12","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:12","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Ses riches sont pleins de violence,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Ses habitants prof\u00e8rent le mensonge,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et leur langue n\u2019est que tromperie dans leur bouche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.13","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:13","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.11","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.13","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:13","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi je te frapperai par la souffrance,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je te ravagerai \u00e0 cause de tes p\u00e9ch\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.14","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.12","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.14","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:14","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Tu mangeras sans te rassasier,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et la faim sera au-dedans de toi;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu mettras en r\u00e9serve et tu ne sauveras pas,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ce que tu sauveras, je le livrerai \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.15","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:15","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.13","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:13","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.15","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:15","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.006.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Tu s\u00e8meras, et tu ne moissonneras pas,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu presseras l\u2019olive, et tu ne feras pas d\u2019onctions avec l\u2019huile,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Tu presseras le mo\u00fbt, et tu ne boiras pas le vin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.16","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:16","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.14","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.16","label":"","reference":"Mich\u00e9e 6:16","prev_osis_id":"Mic.006.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mic.007.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Mic.6.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>On observe les coutumes d\u2019Omri<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et toute la mani\u00e8re d\u2019agir de la maison d\u2019Achab,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et vous marchez d\u2019apr\u00e8s leurs conseils;<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">C\u2019est pourquoi je te livrerai \u00e0 la destruction,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Je ferai de tes habitants un sujet de raillerie,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et vous porterez l\u2019opprobre de mon peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mic.6","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.7.1","name":"Mich\u00e9e 7:1","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.7.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mic.6.15","name":"Mich\u00e9e 6:15","id":"fra-LSG:Mic.6.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript 